angstd.model.arrangement
Class ArrangementManager

java.lang.Object
  angstd.model.arrangement.ArrangementManager

public class ArrangementManager
extends java.lang.Object

Class ArrangementManager can store arrangements and provides methods to retrieve statistical information about the dataset. For instance number of single and multidomains.

Author:
Andreas Held
